      <button>
        Sign up
      </button>
    </p>
  </form>
</div>

<p>There are other form controls available, but we‚Äôve covered the ones who‚Äôll mostly use.</p>

<p>It‚Äôs time to start <strong>styling</strong> our page.</p>
